  "description": "你没看错，这里是新浪科技，不是新浪娱乐。<b>之所以在这里写一篇电影评论，是因为这部电影只有一个主角：谷歌。对，这是一部谷歌想要的形象与招聘广告片。</b>广受瞩目的硅谷主题电影《Internship》昨天开始在美国上映，国内翻译为《挨踢实习生》或者《实习大叔》，讲述了两个失业的豪华表推销员在穷困潦倒 之际突发奇想申请了谷歌夏季实习生项目(居然还成功了！)，来到硅谷谷歌总部开始了一段神奇的实习经历。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d082070/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240524.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E6%8C%A8%E8%B8%A2%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%B1%E8%AF%84%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E7%89%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240524.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E6%8C%A8%E8%B8%A2%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%B1%E8%AF%84%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E7%89%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240524.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E6%8C%A8%E8%B8%A2%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%B1%E8%AF%84%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E7%89%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240524.htm&amp;t=%E3%80%8A%E6%8C%A8%E8%B8%A2%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%B1%E8%AF%84%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E7%89%87\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3